  {
    "client_msg_id": "15461cd3-4d53-4230-b195-a9e7c11bc2ff",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "The other aspect that Emacs shares with WordStar is what <@U013ZLJARC7> has pointed out: rewarding mastery. Much of today's software is designed for low engagement. Worse, engagement is punished by frequent redesigns.",
